# Simon Game - Render Deployment Configuration
# ============================================
# This file documents the production deployment on Render.com
# Last updated: 2026-01-11

## Production URLs
# ----------------
# Frontend (Game):  https://simon-game-frontend-rbvx.onrender.com
# Backend (API):    https://simon-game-backend-8pyb.onrender.com
# Health Check:     https://simon-game-backend-8pyb.onrender.com/health

## Render Services
# ----------------

### Backend Service: simon-game-backend
# Type:           Web Service
# Service ID:     srv-d5hp10l6ubrc7385gb5g
# Dashboard:      https://dashboard.render.com/web/srv-d5hp10l6ubrc7385gb5g
# URL:            https://simon-game-backend-8pyb.onrender.com
# Runtime:        Node.js (20.x via .node-version)
# Region:         Oregon (us-west)
# Plan:           Starter
# Branch:         main
# Auto Deploy:    Yes (on commit)
# Build Command:  npm install && npm run build
# Start Command:  npm start
# Health Check:   /health

### Backend Environment Variables:
# NODE_ENV=production
# PORT=10000
# JWT_SECRET=<generated-secret>
# FRONTEND_URL=https://simon-game-frontend-rbvx.onrender.com

### Frontend Service: simon-game-frontend
# Type:           Static Site
# Service ID:     srv-d5houiq4d50c7397lrf0
# Dashboard:      https://dashboard.render.com/static/srv-d5houiq4d50c7397lrf0
# URL:            https://simon-game-frontend-rbvx.onrender.com
# Plan:           Starter
# Branch:         main
# Auto Deploy:    Yes (on commit)
# Build Command:  cd frontend && npm install && npm run build
# Publish Path:   frontend/dist

### Frontend Environment Variables:
# VITE_API_URL=https://simon-game-backend-8pyb.onrender.com
# VITE_SOCKET_URL=https://simon-game-backend-8pyb.onrender.com

## GitHub Repository
# ------------------
# Repository:     https://github.com/orimi-wix/simon-game-app
# Branch:         main

## Deployment Notes
# -----------------
# - Uses Node.js 20.x LTS (specified in .node-version file)
# - Backend runs on port 10000 (Render default)
# - WebSocket connections use the same backend URL
# - CORS is configured to allow the frontend URL
# - JWT tokens are used for session management (HTTP-only cookies)

## Troubleshooting
# ----------------
# - Check build logs: Dashboard > Deploys > Select deploy > View logs
# - Check runtime logs: Dashboard > Logs
# - Health check endpoint: GET /health
# - If builds fail with npm errors, try triggering a manual deploy

## Manual Deploy Trigger
# ----------------------
# To trigger a manual deploy, update any environment variable or use:
# Render Dashboard > Manual Deploy > Deploy latest commit

